### CodeReview AI — API Request Examples
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or IntelliJ HTTP Client
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000

### ==========================================================================
### Health Check
### ==========================================================================

GET http://localhost:5000/health
Content-Type: application/json

### ==========================================================================
### Auth: GitHub OAuth Callback
### (Requires a valid GitHub OAuth code — get one from the frontend OAuth flow)
### ==========================================================================

POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/github/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "YOUR_GITHUB_OAUTH_CODE_HERE"
}

### ==========================================================================
### Submit a Code Review (SKIP_AUTH=true mode — no token needed)
### ==========================================================================

POST http://localhost:5000/api/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "import os\n\ndef process_data(items=[]):\n    password = 'admin123'\n    query = \"SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = \" + user_id\n    try:\n        result = do_something()\n    except:\n        pass\n    while True:\n        print('running')\n    return items",
    "language": "python"
}

### ==========================================================================
### Poll for Review Results
### (Replace <review_id> with the actual ID from the submit response)
### ==========================================================================

GET http://localhost:5000/api/review/<review_id>
Content-Type: application/json

### ==========================================================================
### Get Review History (Paginated)
### ==========================================================================

GET http://localhost:5000/api/history?page=1&per_page=10
Content-Type: application/json

### ==========================================================================
### Get Aggregate Stats
### ==========================================================================

GET http://localhost:5000/api/stats
Content-Type: application/json

### ==========================================================================
### Submit with JWT Token (when SKIP_AUTH is not set)
### (Replace <your_jwt_token> with the token from the auth callback)
### ==========================================================================

POST http://localhost:5000/api/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <your_jwt_token>

{
    "code": "def hello():\n    print('world')",
    "language": "python"
}

### ==========================================================================
### Error Cases — Input Validation
### ==========================================================================

### Missing code field
POST http://localhost:5000/api/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "language": "python"
}

### Non-JSON body
POST http://localhost:5000/api/review
Content-Type: text/plain

This is not JSON
